<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>

<section class="prose my-6">
  <p>You can use one of the two classes: <code>alert</code> or <code>alert-dialog</code> with any of the following children:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A svg icon,</li>
    <li>A <code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> for the title.</li>
    <li>A <code>&lt;section&gt;</code> for the description. This can include paragraphs, lists, etc.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

